(1323, '075155104X#978-0-7515-5104-4', 'От издателя:An erotic novel of discipline, love and surrender from master storyteller Anne Rice. This sequel to The Claiming of Sleeping Beauty resumes Beauty\'s explicit, teasing exploration of the psychology of human desire and seduction. Now Beauty, having indulged in a secret and forbidden infatuation with the rebellious slave Prince Tristan, is sent away. Sold at auction, she will soon experience the tantalizing punishments of \'the village,\' as her education in love, cruelty, dominance, submission and tenderness is turned over to the brazenly handsome Captain of the Guard. Once again Anne Rice\'s classic tale of pleasure and pain dares to explore the most primal and well-hidden desires of the human heart. This is the second of Anne Rice\'s classic Sleeping Beauty trilogy.The Second in the Classic Sleeping Beauty Trilogy.', 17, '1539', 1703, 'https://img.yakaboo.ua/media/catalog/product/cache/1/image/200x300/234c7c011ba026e66d29567e1be1d1f7/4/4/445223_57718843.jpg', 'Sleeping Beauty. Book 2. Beauty’s Punishment', 118, 'Энн Райс', '', '', '180 гр.', '', '2012', '1984', '20-е', 'Sphere', '', '', '', '', '256 стр.', '', '', 'Современная литература', 'Литература США и Канады', '', '', 'Мягкий', '', '', '', '', 'Sleeping Beauty Trilogy', '', '', 'Бумажная', '', '125x195 мм', '', 'Английский'),
