(1325, '0751551031#978-0-7515-5103-7', 'От издателя:An erotic novel of discipline, love and surrender from master storyteller Anne Rice. In the traditional fairy tale of \'Sleeping Beauty\' the spell cast upon the lovely young princess can only be broken by the kiss of a prince. However, in the world of Anne Rice, this legendary curse is broken not with a kiss, but with sexual initiation. The Prince\'s reward for ending the hundred years of enchantment is Beauty\'s complete and total enslavement to him. Sleeping Beauty awakes to a world of seduction, desire and love. In the first of a three part retelling of the Sleeping Beauty story, Anne Rice explores the unspoken implications of this lush, suggestive fairy tale, opening up a world of erotic yearning and fantasy which is perfect for fans of Fifty Shades of Grey. This is the first of Anne Rice\'s classic Sleeping Beauty trilogy.The First in the Classic Sleeping Beauty Trilogy.', 17, '1535', 1699, 'https://img.yakaboo.ua/media/catalog/product/cache/1/image/200x300/234c7c011ba026e66d29567e1be1d1f7/4/4/445221_59483500.jpg', 'Sleeping Beauty. Book 1. The Claiming of Sleeping Beauty', 118, 'Энн Райс', '', '', '200 гр.', '', '2012', '1983', '21-е', 'Sphere', '', '', '', '', '288 стр.', '', '', 'Современная литература', 'Литература США и Канады', '', '', 'Мягкий', '', '', '', '', 'Sleeping Beauty Trilogy', '', '', 'Бумажная', '', '125x195 мм', '', 'Английский'),
